22
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:37,200
If I have only two soul rings, indeed I did lose.

23
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,780
White Tiger Vajra Transformation.

24
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,140
Is this the millennium soul ring?

25
00:02:52,890 --> 00:02:53,680
Brother.

26
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,910
There isn’t any girl who dislikes roses.

27
00:02:55,930 --> 00:02:58,760
If you’re doing this, how can you get your wife then?

28
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:04,870
Xiao Wu, I think it’s a mistake to
listen to you and come here.

29
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,480
This is a hair crystal.

30
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,100
But how much is it?

31
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:12,890
It’s not expensive. 100 gold soul coins.

32
00:03:12,890 --> 00:03:14,210
Okay. I’ll buy it.

33
00:03:14,210 --> 00:03:15,410
That is not enough.

34
00:03:15,410 --> 00:03:19,000
I’m selling it for 200 gold soul coins.

35
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,870
You’re cheating!

36
00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:24,120
Okay, 500 gold soul coins.
No change.

37
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:49,450
[Soul Land]
[Episode 12]

38
00:03:55,130 --> 00:03:57,530
If you don’t have enough money,

39
00:03:57,530 --> 00:04:00,020
I can only collect 200 gold soul coins first.

40
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:03,680
You can pay the remaining

41
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:06,750
for 10 coins monthly with 10% of interest.

42
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:10,410
<i>10 coins per month?
He knows I’m a soul master.</i>

43
00:04:10,410 --> 00:04:14,090
<i>I didn’t feel the soul power of him.</i>

44
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:16,090
Little San!

45
00:04:16,090 --> 00:04:17,070
Deal.

46
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,750
Where did you get this belt?

47
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:32,940
My master gave it to me. Do you know it?

48
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:34,780
Do you want to change the price again?

49
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,820
You are his student?

50
00:04:37,910 --> 00:04:40,830
Take the crystal with you.

51
00:04:41,710 --> 00:04:44,630
I will send 10 gold soul coins to you every week.

52
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:46,100
No need. I’ll give it to you for free.

53
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,250
For free?

54
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:51,840
It wasn’t something valuable. Just go.

55
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:54,000
Don’t disturb my sleeping.

56
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:57,060
<i>Does he know Master?</i>

57
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:02,990
Little San, let’s go!

58
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:04,500
Xiao Wu.

59
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:07,640
Uncle, please offer a price.

60
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:31,640
Grandmaster. Aren’t you going to
hide from me this time?

61
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,450
Hurry up, Xiao Wu.

62
00:06:17,450 --> 00:06:19,810
Hurry up and help me collect
all these golden granules.

63
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:21,100
Don’t miss even one.

64
00:06:29,970 --> 00:06:32,830
Brother. What on Earth is this crystal?

65
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:34,690
You look anxious and excited.

66
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:37,360
This is not an ordinary crystal.
This is a hair crystal.

67
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,660
Hair crystal?

68
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,730
Some crystals will form
golden silk threads inside...

69
00:06:40,730 --> 00:06:43,440
when they are affected by external forces.

70
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:46,800
These golden silk threads are so resilient

71
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,510
with strong elasticity, so it’s called hair gold.

72
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:51,970
The crystal that forms hair gold
is called hair crystal.

73
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:57,340
Hair gold and hair crystal.
What do they do?

74
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:06,430
This is...

75
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,670
Without the crystal’s protection,

76
00:07:07,670 --> 00:07:10,410
hair gold will curl up to form granules.

77
00:07:10,410 --> 00:07:13,640
It will revert to hair gold
when the soul power is injected.

78
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:15,630
Then?

79
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:20,380
I estimate this hair crystal is
at least 100,000 years old.

80
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:23,310
It’s the best hair crystal, plate crystal.

81
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:25,590
So, what can they do?

82
00:07:25,590 --> 00:07:27,780
Don’t worry, look.

83
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:34,990
I still don’t get it.

84
00:07:34,990 --> 00:07:36,940
Do you remember the hidden weapon
that I told you?

85
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:39,290
Hair gold is thinner and sharper than needle.

86
00:07:39,290 --> 00:07:42,320
Its puncture ability gets more powerful
after soul power is injected.

87
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,510
Its size is small.

88
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:46,370
Let’s imagine. If it penetrates into the body,

89
00:07:46,370 --> 00:07:51,000
what is the effect if the hair gold
curls up when it losses the soul power?

90
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:58,910
If this penetrates into a human body...

91
00:08:21,490 --> 00:08:23,270
When the hair gold penetrates
into the human body,

92
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:25,250
unless using some special tactics,

93
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:29,200
otherwise, you’ll have to cut off
the muscles that are curled up...

94
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,200
to take it out.

95
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:36,490
This is a natural hidden weapon.

96
00:08:36,490 --> 00:08:39,280
I call it Dragon Beard Needle.

97
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:43,910
<i>The eighth in Xuan Tian Records that
is specialized to break the radon.</i>

98
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:52,230
Brother. This hidden weapon is too vicious.

99
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:58,130
In this world, it’s not the weapon...

100
00:08:58,130 --> 00:09:02,430
that decides its vice.
It’s up to the person who uses it.

101
00:09:02,430 --> 00:09:05,450
It’ll be good if it’s correctly used.
It’ll be vicious if it’s violated.

102
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:07,550
If it’s used to punish the wicked,

103
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:09,700
it will be perfect.

104
00:09:20,330 --> 00:09:24,610
Xiao Wu, you’ve grown up.
It’s not that you can’t walk.

105
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:26,910
I don’t care. You are my brother.

106
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:28,830
Didn’t Grandmaster say that...

107
00:09:28,830 --> 00:09:32,570
Shrek School can be seen not far
from the south gate of Suo Tuo?

108
00:09:32,570 --> 00:09:34,540
We have walked so far.

109
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:36,540
Why aren’t we reaching yet?

110
00:09:36,540 --> 00:09:38,130
I am carrying you on my back.

111
00:09:38,130 --> 00:09:40,110
When did you walk so far?

112
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:42,060
Why I don’t know it?

113
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:45,790
Yes. You walked so far.

114
00:09:57,090 --> 00:09:59,160
Brother. Look in front.

115
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:27,180
[Soul Land]

116
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:43,460
It’s impossible. This is a soul master school?

117
00:10:43,460 --> 00:10:46,200
Brother. Did Grandmaster make a mistake?

118
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:51,380
It doesn’t look like a school here. Is this a deceit?

119
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:54,010
Since we’re here, let’s have a look.

120
00:10:54,010 --> 00:10:58,730
Is anything wrong? This is
the so-called soul master school?

121
00:10:58,730 --> 00:11:01,970
It even claims that students would
be a viscount after graduation.

122
00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:03,510
People from the Martial Soul Hall said it.

123
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:04,870
It should be right.

124
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:07,720
But...this school looks really old.

125
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,550
Father, I don’t want to study here.
It’s so embarrassing!

126
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:12,740
Let me go to Suo Tuo Intermediate
Soul Master School.

127
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:15,710
I was also considered a genius
in the Beginner School.

128
00:11:15,710 --> 00:11:18,710
Since we’re here, let’s just wait.

129
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:20,700
Maybe this is a test.

130
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:23,200
The real school is not located here.

131
00:11:26,650 --> 00:11:29,500
Teacher, here is 10 gold soul coins.

132
00:11:30,410 --> 00:11:32,590
Reach out a hand.

133
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:40,670
Your age doesn’t match. You can go now.

134
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:43,990
Teacher, my son has just passed
the age of admission.

135
00:11:43,990 --> 00:11:46,410
Can you please make an exception?

136
00:11:47,830 --> 00:11:53,150
Based on the school rules, admission is
not allowed beyond the age of admission.

137
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,840
You knew it.

138
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:57,780
Then, our admission fees...

139
00:11:57,780 --> 00:12:00,300
After registration, admission fees
are not refundable.

140
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:05,090
Not refundable?
You are cheating for money!

141
00:12:05,090 --> 00:12:08,330
Hurry up and go! Don’t affect the people behind.

142
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:09,070
No way!

143
00:12:09,070 --> 00:12:12,490
You must make refund!
Otherwise, I’m not leaving!

144
00:12:12,490 --> 00:12:14,650
If we know Shrek School is so poor,

145
00:12:14,650 --> 00:12:16,210
we shouldn’t come!

146
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:28,920
Mu Bai, someone is claiming for
a refund. Settle it.

147
00:12:29,350 --> 00:12:31,990
You can have a refund.

148
00:12:41,190 --> 00:12:44,130
Fully refund if he can win me in a battle.

149
00:12:46,990 --> 00:12:49,870
It’s purple! It’s a millennium one!

150
00:12:58,650 --> 00:13:00,640
We’re so unlucky! Let’s go!

151
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:08,590
Failed. You can go now.

152
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:11,220
Why? My son is perfectly good.

153
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:13,450
He’s an outstanding student in
the Beginner Soul Master School.

154
00:13:13,450 --> 00:13:15,610
Moreover, he has a century soul ring.

155
00:13:15,610 --> 00:13:17,560
It’s rare to own a century soul ring.

156
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:21,130
It’s good to own one.

157
00:13:21,130 --> 00:13:23,280
But judged from his soul power,

158
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:25,380
he’s just an ordinary person.

159
00:13:25,380 --> 00:13:27,450
I don’t understand.

160
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:35,290
When you register at Shrek School,

161
00:13:35,290 --> 00:13:37,380
you should be clear with the rules.

162
00:13:37,950 --> 00:13:40,410
If you come here without figuring it out,

163
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:43,150
you’re just paying the admission fees for nothing.

164
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:50,320
It’s still not too late to leave if you regret.

165
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:56,190
Do you know the meaning of Shrek?

166
00:13:56,190 --> 00:13:59,370
Shrek is a monster.

167
00:13:59,370 --> 00:14:04,310
It’s extremely weird among the soul beasts.

168
00:14:04,310 --> 00:14:06,380
The meaning of Shrek School...

169
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:08,250
is a monster school.

170
00:14:08,250 --> 00:14:11,820
We only accept “monsters” but not ordinary people.

171
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,780
Anyone who exceeds the age of admission...

172
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:17,080
or soul power below Level 21,

173
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:19,620
you don’t have to waste your time here.

174
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:21,270
<i>Only accept “monsters”?</i>

175
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:28,180
<i>He is a Soul Emperor?</i>

176
00:14:37,900 --> 00:14:39,490
Next!

177
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:42,910
This school looks interesting.

178
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:45,100
Especially when that teacher said...

179
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:48,690
they only accept “monsters”
but not an ordinary one. Awesome.

180
00:14:48,690 --> 00:14:51,280
Now, you don’t doubt Master’s order, right?

181
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:53,880
Shrek School must be unusual.

182
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:05,630
It’s awesome.

183
00:15:26,930 --> 00:15:29,970
Did I pass the preliminary test?

184
00:15:30,850 --> 00:15:33,700
Do your family know you are here?

185
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,300
Instruction knows no class distinction.

186
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:37,350
As long as I meet the school requirements,

187
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:39,350
you have no reason to reject my admission.

188
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:49,200
Come here.

189
00:15:54,070 --> 00:15:55,990
Teacher, the two of us want to register.

190
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:06,230
Your ages fulfilled.

191
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:10,110
Did...

192
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:16,440
Did you learn any soul skill with your hands?

193
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,510
Yes.

194
00:16:19,590 --> 00:16:21,590
Lift your leg.

195
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:31,050
Muscle growth is good.
Bone age is suitable.

196
00:16:31,050 --> 00:16:34,850
Okay. Release your Martial Soul.

197
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,380
Rabbit.

198
00:17:06,930 --> 00:17:11,160
Yours is Blue Silver Plant.

199
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,960
You can practice so fast with Blue Silver Plant.

200
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:15,460
Teacher.

201
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:18,090
Don’t you only accept monster?

202
00:17:18,090 --> 00:17:19,890
Am I a monster?

203
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:27,080
Yes, you are.

204
00:17:27,080 --> 00:17:29,800
Mu Bai. Take them in.

205
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:30,510
Yes.

206
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:33,890
Come on. Follow me.

207
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,320
Thank you.

208
00:17:35,320 --> 00:17:36,830
It’s nothing.

209
00:17:53,130 --> 00:17:53,940
What?

210
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:56,590
Nothing.

211
00:18:09,290 --> 00:18:12,520
What are you looking at?
Any girls do you want to tackle?

212
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:15,100
I felt something just now.

213
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:19,070
This feeling seems to be supplementary
with my Martial Soul.

214
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:22,430
Supplementary?
That’s an excuse.

215
00:18:22,430 --> 00:18:24,170
You must take a fancy to a girl.

216
00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:25,330
You know nothing.

217
00:18:25,330 --> 00:18:26,540
In Martial Soul,

218
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:29,910
it’s hard to find a supplementary Martial Soul.

219
00:18:29,910 --> 00:18:32,690
If you find it and team up,

220
00:18:32,690 --> 00:18:35,690
the strength of Martial Soul
will increase exponentially.

221
00:18:35,690 --> 00:18:38,580
This is called Martial Soul Fusion Skill.

222
00:18:39,170 --> 00:18:40,580
That means...

223
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:43,630
that girl’s Martial Soul must be a tigress.

224
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,540
Maybe.

225
00:19:07,540 --> 00:19:09,960
You will undergo the second exam here.

226
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,830
The teacher will tell you what to do.

227
00:19:12,530 --> 00:19:14,070
I need to go out and check.

228
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:20,320
Sausages! Sausages for sale!

229
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:23,950
Have a look! Oscar sausage!

230
00:19:23,950 --> 00:19:26,610
Delicious and affordable!

231
00:19:26,610 --> 00:19:30,660
There’s also pure and refreshing green tea!

232
00:19:31,390 --> 00:19:32,530
[Sausages for sale]

233
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:15,110
[Next Episode]
Where is my sausage?

234
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:18,600
What happened?
Doesn’t the sausage taste good?

235
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:21,860
Silly.

236
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:23,220
What is this?

237
00:21:23,220 --> 00:21:26,090
Why can they skip the test
to enter the fourth exam?

238
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:29,030
Tang San. Show them your soul power.

239
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:34,800
Teacher Zhao. I bring them here
to undergo the fourth exam.

